t of Agriculture (USDA); United States Forest ServiceRP Duncanson, L (通讯作者)，Univ Maryland, 2181 Lefrak Hall, College Pk, MD 20742 USA.', 'lduncans@umd.eduRI Burslem, David FRP/F-1204-2019; Kljun, Natascha/B-8467-2008; Abril,   Antonio García/F-7267-2016; Boschetti, Luigi/C-6198-2008; Vrska,   Tomas/AAC-9161-2020; Tang, Hao/GPS-5518-2022; Krucek,   Martin/B-9394-2015; Longo, Marcos/F-5033-2014; Erasmus, Barend   FN/G-3411-2012; Krucek, Martin/HKW-7281-2023; Naidoo,   Laven/HJY-7527-2023; Dalponte, Michele/E-5117-2011; Corona,   Piermaria/G-1565-2011; Phillips, Oliver/A-1523-2011; Lewis, Simon   L/I-9025-2012; Hill, Ross A/B-3871-2009; Barbier, Nicolas/A-5489-2010;   Simard, Marc/H-3516-2013; Valbuena, Ruben/I-6127-2019; de Miguel,   Sergio/B-8358-2016; Armston, John/JFS-0209-2023; Goetz, Scott   J/A-3393-2015; Cutler, Mark E.J./I-7123-2012; O\'Brien,   Michael/V-6548-2017; Tanase, Mihai/AAG-8049-2020; Coomes, David   A/H-5630-2011; Poulsen, John/O-5332-2019; Huang, huabing/JHT-7278-2023;   TORRESAN, Chiara/Q-4939-2018', 'Burslem, David FRP/0000-0001-6033-0990; Kljun,   Natascha/0000-0001-9650-2184; Abril, Antonio García/0000-0002-5040-7867;   Boschetti, Luigi/0000-0001-6525-4413; Tang, Hao/0000-0001-7935-5848;   Krucek, Martin/0000-0002-3137-2259; Longo, Marcos/0000-0001-5062-6245;   Erasmus, Barend FN/0000-0003-1869-8091; Krucek,   Martin/0000-0002-3137-2259; Dalponte, Michele/0000-0001-9850-8985;   Corona, Piermaria/0000-0002-8105-0792; Phillips,   Oliver/0000-0002-8993-6168; Barbier, Nicolas/0000-0002-5323-3866;   Simard, Marc/0000-0002-9442-4562; Valbuena, Ruben/0000-0003-0493-7581;   de Miguel, Sergio/0000-0002-9738-0657; Goetz, Scott   J/0000-0002-6326-4308; Cutler, Mark E.J./0000-0002-3893-1068; O\'Brien,   Michael/0000-0003-0943-8423; Poulsen, John/0000-0002-1532-9808; Huang,   huabing/0000-0001-6253-8437; White, Joanne/0000-0003-4674-0373;   Gobakken, Terje/0000-0001-5534-049X; Kral, Kamil/0000-0002-3848-2119;   Orwig, David/0000-0001-7822-3560; Morsdorf, Fe